data.description: Discover the priceless joy of owning this energy-efficient 2-bed, 2-bath home in Tucson! The fully-fenced single-level residence offers a cozy front porch where you can enjoy your morning coffee. Tastefully renewed interior showcases fresh paint, soft palette, upscale ceiling fans, and travertine flooring in all the right places. Bright living room invites you to relax after a busy day, while the formal dining room with French doors to the back patio is perfect for holding a feast. The galley kitchen comes with ample white cabinetry. Venture to the main bedroom to find wood-look tile floors and a private bathroom. Create lasting memories in the large backyard with a covered patio and mature tree that provides constant shade. This turn-key value awaits you!
